{"tid":756600,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖][航拍][毒遊] 東京&原奧(匈)帝國","createTime":"2018-07-26T07:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T11:56:16.000Z","uid":5547,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fb618c641d9074251c8824ff396816be6259b93e","tid":756600,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:30:46.000Z","msg":"當係咁二講下<br />\n無錯，呢次個行程完全係亂黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過又想去翻日本當補番之前東京未去或去得少既地方<br />\n原本個plan就真係走一轉[原]奧匈帝國<br />\n由一戰觸發地Sarajevo一個圈去到Wien<br />\n但咁太過走馬看花 唔岩我玩法<br />\n結果只決定去羅馬尼亞同匈牙利<br />\n放棄哂Balkans Czech Slovakia<br />\nAustria去過三大城 講真未必有興趣再去Wien<br />\nGraz同Salzburg就真心靚既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n工作關係 <br />\n有個「暑假」六月三十號去到八月十三號<br />\n所以七月一號就出發 二十五號翻<br />\n仲有半個月比我鳩up<br />\n希望時間容許啦<br />\n<br />\n由於日本既行程超過60%含有「劇毒」<br />\n呢度唔係動物台<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只會「係咁二」up下算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行程</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1-6 日本東京</span><br />\n----------------------<br />\nDay 1-3老秋 昭和館 台場<br />\nDay 4 橫須賀 新宿<br />\nDay 5 都係老秋 上野<br />\nDay 6 飛去Moscow後去Bucharest<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7-16 Romania</span><br />\n----------------------<br />\nDay 7-8 Bucharest<br />\nDay 9-10 Sinaia <br />\nDay 11-13 Brașov &amp; Bran<br />\nDay 14-15 Sibiu<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">16-23 Hungary</span><br />\n----------------------<br />\nDay 16-17 Szeged<br />\nDay 18-19 Eger<br />\nDay 20-23 Budapest<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">24 Finland</span><br />\n----------------------<br />\nDay 24 Helsinki<br />\n<br />\n同之前四次歐遊唔同<br />\n只買左兩本Lonely Planet, 睇較有興趣既城市<br />\n係Google map畫畫畫就Go<br />\nPlan? 無喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到邊度就腳咪去邊囉<br />\n行到攰咪去酒吧啤下佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n影相既裝備<br />\niPhone柒<br />\nSony RX100 mkV<br />\nDJI Mavic Pro<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔識影相 隻drone都係六月先買，好少飛既經驗<br />\n影得唔好請屌細力D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東京講到明唔比Drone 所以唔會有Drone相<br />\nBucharest睇Drone forum有人出過事比警察沒收 所以都唔駁啦<br />\n<br />\n係咁二up下航拍既野<br />\n其實 羅馬尼亞同匈牙利 都係有Drone law &amp; regulation<br />\n正常遊客係唔會比你飛<br />\n渣正黎做佢絕對有權充公隻drone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要完全合法飛要<br />\n1) 注冊你隻野 放底90歐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2) 所有飛行時間同航道都要一五一十同國防部報告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(鬼知邊度靚而值得飛起佢咩，時間都無可能預知啦)<br />\n<br />\n3) 唔可以隻Drone離開你既視線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(咪玩啦大佬 60米已經睇唔到佢係邊，影條毛咩？)<br />\n<br />\n4) 通常唔比飛高過100米 <br />\n<br />\n5) 多人就唔比飛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(咁即係基本上得無人荒野飛得呀？)<br />\n<br />\n6) 唔可以夜間飛行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以<br />\n呢個post內既相or片都完全犯足哂上面既野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論係都係quote自Drone forum講<br />\n用Common sense黎飛<br />\nDon&rsquo;t fly stupid <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無人叫你用隻Drone黎入侵國會呀軍事基地呀機場呀架<br />\n有飛機聲都等佢走左先飛啦<br />\n<br />\n求其整幾張先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/6GmLtwLYtPNshmXinG-sO9DAN7XSpBDqFR5o-YLPhWp8BTZzPMPxxKA7t5rkNj3jC-N12A3T87uGJHzgAWFmcwB79khBklooM2AdTKlfdIDfBMOGkyw_V6tJSZ6f2R2BHe8BlEO--6eOdKHMLdSPAEGGVcw_7jb8JTlrorm7ETIL00vUE80LtnFvDBPe8sT9WOu0CJhRthzpEBJVCW27arIUfapRjGu61FXlJtRGpaKdETGaO9gA-lOXsSMtM4PXyu0pFCUPT94DUv8zZYKifomVd-iyuOhn3B0Lh0xpiMj_ac2fa5U5KcfYur2Z0B8YH4QzM1rorRSytpLxRyU4hVstso15eLE5ERNdmUOUwPtjr3hLNpE-h3-jrVYlgISeLAdjU9IXt4z5mBkQjk18c1l2pkS8aakbjSMfo3XE4VS0gpy2q_O3UP8Rlj0ryptTEqsbEDhOQ5gRK8WsWCWB9cmYhK2omXbFaKvrcU